---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'IMG Global in France', level: 2 },
  { id: 'visa-coverage', text: 'Pre-PUMA Visa Coverage', level: 2 },
  { id: 'france-network', text: 'Network Coverage', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'vs-local-options', text: 'vs French Options', level: 2 },
  { id: 'claims', text: 'Using Your Insurance', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-its-for', text: 'Who Should Choose IMG', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'Common Questions', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in France', href: '/countries/france/insurance' },
  { title: 'IMG Global Review', href: '/providers/img-global' },
  { title: 'IMG vs Cigna', href: '/compare/img-global-vs-cigna-global' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'francePrice', header: 'France (Age 40)' },
  { key: 'effectiveDed', header: 'Effective Deductible' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Global Medical Insurance', coverage: 'Inpatient + Outpatient', francePrice: '€110-150/mo', effectiveDed: '50% waiver' },
  { plan: 'With €2,500 Deductible', coverage: 'Inpatient + Outpatient', francePrice: '€80-110/mo', effectiveDed: '€1,250 effective' },
  { plan: 'With €5,000 Deductible', coverage: 'Inpatient + Outpatient', francePrice: '€65-90/mo', effectiveDed: '€2,500 effective' },
  { plan: 'With €10,000 Deductible', coverage: 'Inpatient + Outpatient', francePrice: '€55-75/mo', effectiveDed: '€5,000 effective' },
];

const comparisonColumns = [
  { key: 'factor', header: 'Factor' },
  { key: 'img', header: 'IMG Global' },
  { key: 'french', header: 'French System' },
];

const comparisonRows = [
  { factor: 'Monthly Cost (Age 40)', img: '€110-150', french: '€50-150 (mutuelle)' },
  { factor: 'With High Deductible', img: '€55-90', french: 'N/A' },
  { factor: 'Deductible Waiver', img: '50% outside US', french: 'No' },
  { factor: 'Pre-PUMA Coverage', img: 'Full coverage', french: 'Not available' },
  { factor: 'Annual Maximum', img: 'Up to $8M', french: 'Unlimited (PUMA)' },
  { factor: 'Medical Evacuation', img: 'Up to $500K', french: 'Not included' },
  { factor: 'Portability', img: 'Worldwide', french: 'France only' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="IMG Global Health Insurance in France"
  description="Complete guide to using IMG Global in France. Budget-friendly international coverage with the 50% deductible waiver advantage."
  headline="IMG Global Health Insurance in France"
  subheadline="Budget-friendly international coverage for expats in France. How IMG's 50% deductible waiver works for pre-PUMA coverage."
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/france-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get an IMG France Quote"
  ctaButtonHref="/providers/img-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">IMG Global in France</h2>
  <p>
    IMG Global offers a budget-friendly path to international health insurance for expats in France. Their high-deductible options and 50% deductible waiver make them one of the most affordable international options for the pre-PUMA period.
  </p>
  <p>
    The strategy: use IMG for visa compliance and initial coverage, then transition to PUMA + mutuelle when eligible (3+ months).
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$8M</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Max annual limit</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">50%</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Deductible waiver outside US</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$500K</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Medical evacuation</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Get a France-Specific Quote"
    description="See what IMG Global costs for expats living in France."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/providers/img-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="visa-coverage">Pre-PUMA Visa Coverage</h2>
  <p>
    IMG Global can be used for French visa applications, though it's less commonly used than Cigna or Allianz. Verify acceptance with your specific consulate.
  </p>

  <h3>Visa Requirements</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Comprehensive inpatient and outpatient coverage</li>
    <li>Valid for the full visa duration</li>
    <li>Adequate coverage limits (IMG offers up to $8M)</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-2">Verify First</h3>
    <p class="text-yellow-800">
      IMG is less commonly used for French visas. Confirm acceptance with your consulate before purchasing. For visa certainty, consider Cigna or Allianz which are more established for French applications.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="france-network">Network Coverage in France</h2>
  <p>
    IMG uses primarily a reimbursement model in France. Pay providers directly, then submit claims.
  </p>

  <h3>How It Works</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Any licensed provider:</strong> See any French doctor or hospital</li>
    <li><strong>Pay and submit:</strong> Reimbursement typically in 5-10 days</li>
    <li><strong>Freedom:</strong> No network restrictions</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <p>
    <em>Prices for worldwide coverage excluding USA. Age 40 shown.</em>
  </p>

  <h3>The 50% Deductible Waiver</h3>
  <p>
    IMG's standout feature: treatment outside the US gets 50% off your deductible. In France:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>€5,000 deductible → €2,500 effective</strong> in France</li>
    <li><strong>€2,500 deductible → €1,250 effective</strong> in France</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Calculate Your Savings"
    description="See how much you can save with IMG's high-deductible options."
    buttonText="Get a Quote"
    buttonHref="/providers/img-global"
  />

  <h2 id="vs-local-options">vs French Options</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={comparisonColumns} rows={comparisonRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Use IMG Global If:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Budget is a major consideration</li>
    <li>High-deductible strategy appeals to you</li>
    <li>You're comfortable with reimbursement</li>
    <li>You travel outside France frequently</li>
    <li>Medical evacuation is important</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Switch to PUMA + Mutuelle If:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>You're eligible (3+ months residency)</li>
    <li>You want French system integration</li>
    <li>Budget is a concern</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    <a href="/countries/france/insurance">See all France insurance options →</a>
  </p>

  <h2 id="claims">Using Your Insurance in France</h2>

  <h3>Reimbursement Process</h3>
  <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
    <li>See any licensed provider</li>
    <li>Pay at time of service (get facture)</li>
    <li>Submit via IMG app or portal</li>
    <li>Processing: 5-10 business days</li>
    <li>Reimbursement in euros</li>
  </ol>

  <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Should Choose IMG in France</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Good Fit</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>Budget-conscious expats</li>
        <li>Healthy individuals</li>
        <li>Those comfortable with reimbursement</li>
        <li>Expats who travel frequently</li>
        <li>Short-term pre-PUMA coverage needs</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Consider Alternatives</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Those wanting guaranteed visa acceptance</li>
        <li>Expats with pre-existing conditions</li>
        <li>Those needing mental health coverage</li>
        <li>Long-term France residents</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="faqs">Common Questions</h2>

  <h3>Is IMG accepted for French visas?</h3>
  <p>
    IMG can be used, but it's less established than Cigna or Allianz for French visas. Verify with your consulate.
  </p>

  <h3>How does the 50% deductible waiver work?</h3>
  <p>
    Treatment outside the US automatically gets 50% off your deductible. A €5,000 deductible becomes €2,500 in France.
  </p>

  <h3>Should I switch to PUMA after 3 months?</h3>
  <p>
    For most expats, yes. PUMA + mutuelle is typically cheaper and well-integrated with French healthcare. Keep IMG only if you travel frequently or might relocate.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready for Budget-Friendly Coverage?"
    description="Get a personalized IMG Global quote for France."
    buttonText="Get Your Quote"
    buttonHref="/providers/img-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This guide is for informational purposes only. Visa requirements and PUMA rules change. Verify all information with IMG Global and French authorities.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
